item.title: CVE-2016-10541|2024-08-06T03:21:52.153Z -- hackerone -- shell-quote%20node%20module
item.description: The npm module "shell-quote" 1.6.0 and earlier cannot correctly escape ">" and "<" operator used for redirection in shell. Applications that depend on shell-quote may also be vulnerable. A malicious user could perform code injection.
